{"acceptance_criteria":"","actor":"","agent_state":"","assignee":null,"await_id":"","await_type":"","close_reason":"Fixed: switched to async PeriodicReader + reqwest-client + explicit /v1/metrics path + numeric prefix parsing","closed_at":"2026-03-14T22:23:32Z","closed_by_session":"","compacted_at":null,"compacted_at_commit":null,"compaction_level":0,"content_hash":"47b0b4cf79de28ee69baedc33017b20a455c3696ecbbd5a5657bd18a75277efe","created_at":"2026-03-14T21:52:45Z","created_by":"Christoph Neumüller","crystallizes":0,"defer_until":null,"description":"The opentelemetry-otlp v0.31 (latest) OTLP/HTTP export never actually sends metrics to the collector. Tested extensively with otel-collector-contrib:\n\n- reqwest-blocking-client without rt-tokio: PeriodicReader thread runs but HttpClient trait is async, so export silently fails. force_flush() returns InternalFailure.\n- reqwest-blocking-client with rt-tokio: PeriodicReader's std::thread panics 'no reactor running' since thread doesn't inherit tokio context.\n- reqwest-client (async) with rt-tokio: Same thread-context issue.\n- experimental_metrics_periodicreader_with_async_runtime + rt-tokio + reqwest-client: PeriodicReader spawns tokio task, no panics, force_flush() returns Ok, but zero TCP connections to collector and zero metrics received.\n\nRust 1.94.0, OTel SDK 0.31.0 are both latest. This is an architectural issue in the SDK, not a version lag. Fix options: (1) switch to grpc-tonic transport, (2) manually POST OTLP payloads with reqwest, (3) wait for upstream fix (see open-telemetry/opentelemetry-rust#3125).","design":"","due_at":null,"ephemeral":0,"estimated_minutes":null,"event_kind":"","external_ref":null,"hook_bead":"","id":"lox-bp8","is_template":0,"issue_type":"bug","last_activity":null,"metadata":"{}","mol_type":"","no_history":0,"notes":"","original_size":null,"owner":"c.neumueller@gmail.com","payload":"","pinned":0,"priority":2,"quality_score":null,"rig":"","role_bead":"","role_type":"","sender":"","source_repo":"","source_system":"","spec_id":"","status":"closed","target":"","timeout_ns":0,"title":"OTel OTLP export broken: PeriodicReader + reqwest-blocking-client incompatible","updated_at":"2026-03-14T22:23:32Z","waiters":"","wisp_type":"","work_type":""}
